sentence: When we grow up, many of us dream of going on an adventurous journey to distant lands. For instance, Myanmar often rings a bell as a fascinating place to visit. sentence: In four days' time, a group of students will start their adventurous journey to Myanmar. So far, they have planned to explore the beautiful pagodas and wander through the bustling markets. Now and two years from now, they hope this trip will become a cherished memory, as they walk up and down the scenic trails and connect with the local culture.

2.answer: The beautiful pagodas and bustling markets
